{"type": "article", "id": 17263, "title": "Marc Newson 的水壶和面包机组合", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-09T07:10:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606140503n2MrEVqCWKhgOAbF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一套不锈钢的水壶和面包机组合，是 Marc Newson 首次与澳大利亚厨卫品牌Sunbeam 的合作。拉丝不锈钢的材质主体让它们有 Marc Newson一贯的未来感，水壶盖上和面包机身使用了其他颜色，有的甚至很鲜艳，在贴近生活之中也满足了不同的人群。此外，两个家电的外形都偏扁圆，小巧而有一种复古感。共有红、橙、黄、绿、蓝、黑、白 7 种颜色，<a href=\"http://www.sunbeam.com.au/Marc-Newson-Kettle.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">每件产品分别售价 199 美元，这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144350fd8mT0ZOQCsK6bNh.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144351s2y4QTYGg8cOVX3a.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144351yLP9XvsKRSTE31Vu.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144352rkpRVf4nYjt9KSxq.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"518\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5534188\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144353MHRr6xKXkbhYLmdi.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}